"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-now-approximately-5-years-old-heres-next-5-years/\">UpdraftPlus is now (approximately) 5 years old. Here&#8217;s to the next 5 years&#8230;</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Romelch Otic\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2653:\"<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">We&#8217;re not sure what to call UpdraftPlus&#8217;s actual birthday. If we&#8217;re going to be picky, 5 years ago was only the date when the UpdraftPlus.com brand was born.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">The backup plugin it was based on was around before; it was originally released 8 years ago as Updraft. Then 6 ½ years ago, our lead developer David Anderson took it on, tweaking, updating and adding extra features to turn it into the UpdraftPlus we have today.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">We haven&#8217;t been able to leave our baby alone. We&#8217;re thrilled at all your feedback and how much over a million websites have now embraced us.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">But there&#8217;s always more we can do: we&#8217;ve extended our team, drawing in global talent to expand UpdraftPlus&#8217; features and capabilities and to optimise its design and usability. Plus, alongside all of the little general/ compatibility fixes we keep on top of, we&#8217;re constantly making little tweaks and adjustments that all contribute to making backing up smoother, easier and more flexible.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">Plus, we&#8217;ve made a few acquisitions along the way: we now own WP Optimize, which helps websites to run at optimal efficiency without the need for manual requests, MetaSlider, which makes adding attractive sliders to websites child&#8217;s play, and most recently, Easy Updates Manager, which puts you in control of automating updates for WordPress core, themes and plugins. We&#8217;ve developed a Premium version of WP Optimize, which is due to be released soon alongside our best-ever new release of UpdraftCentral.</p>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: left;\">The UpdraftPlus family is growing fast, and it&#8217;s all-hands-on-deck as we maintain the very highest standards and seek to give our customers the best user experience. We&#8217;d like to thank you once again for your loyalty. Please keep your feedback, ideas and suggestions coming- we love hearing from you. After all, without you, UpdraftPlus would be nothing.</p>\n<span class=\"et_bloom_bottom_trigger\"></span><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-now-approximately-5-years-old-heres-next-5-years/\">UpdraftPlus is now (approximately) 5 years old. Here&#8217;s to the next 5 years&#8230;</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-now-approximately-5-years-old-heres-next-5-years/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"commen