een growing steadily to 14 at UpdraftPlus as we take on more plugins like WP-Optimize, MetaSlider and now Easy Updates Manager, and should grow further throughout 2018. As a result we have a vacancy! Do you have &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/vacancy-head-testing-updraftplus/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/vacancy-head-testing-updraftplus/\">Vacancy for Head of Testing at UpdraftPlus</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Joe Miles\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1152:\"<p>Our team has been growing steadily to 14 at UpdraftPlus as we take on more plugins like WP-Optimize, MetaSlider and now Easy Updates Manager, and should grow further throughout 2018.</p>\n<p>As a result we have a vacancy!</p>\n<p>Do you have an eye for detail and a great knowledge of WordPress?  Can you see things from the user&#8217;s perspective and know what to suggest to make things &#8216;just work&#8217;?</p>\n<p>Then if you&#8217;d like to work freelance, and part or full time as a head of testing for UpdraftPlus family of plugins, then let me know: business-management@updraftplus.com</p>\n<p>Knowledge of code or using a version control system (we use Gitlab like Git) would be an advantage, although it&#8217;s not essential for this role.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<span class=\"et_bloom_bottom_trigger\"></span><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"h